description.en: MSN, a multidimensional sustainable business public blockchain, combines the NFC traceability technology with blockchain technology for the first time, applies it to tea industry, and ensures the traceability information can’t be tampered with and is just. At the same time, it provides supply chain finance and supply chain management of tea industry with solutions and optimize industry structure of tea industry by utilizing top technological models such as on-chain OTR and ZERO knowledge proof and warehouse management network proof. MSN will also land ecological landing application such as AI mining machines of making tea and tea exchange, and it will have important meaning for global tea industry and other industries and commerce.
